---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cases — PWA's, Automatisering en Design | Webbiecorn">
  <style>
    #cases-main { background: var(--black-mid); }
    #cases-cta { background: var(--black); padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    .cases-full-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    .case-card-full {
      background: var(--black-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.25s, border-color 0.3s;
      color: var(--white); display: block;
      position: relative; text-decoration: none;
    }
    .case-card-full::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 3px; background: var(--red);
      transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left; transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .case-card-full:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
    .case-card-full:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); border-color: rgba(217,43,75,0.3); }
    .case-visual {
      height: 220px;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--black-mid);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .case-visual img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }
    .case-card-full:hover .case-visual img { transform: scale(1.05); }
    .case-body { padding: 1.5rem 2rem 2rem; }
    .case-status {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .case-status.live { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.15); color: #4ade80; border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.25); }
    .case-status.concept { background: rgba(217,43,75,0.12); color: var(--red); border: 1px solid rgba(217,43,75,0.25); }
    .case-status.lopend { background: rgba(251,191,36,0.12); color: #fbbf24; border: 1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.25); }
    .case-card-full .case-title { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
    .case-card-full .case-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .case-card-full .case-tag { color: var(--red); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .proof-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .proof-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.2rem 1.25rem;
    }
    .proof-kicker {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1.8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--red);
      margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    }
    .proof-value {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .proof-copy {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">Het lab</p>
    <h1 class="page-hero-title reveal reveal-delay-1">Werk dat laat zien<br/><em>hoe wij denken.</em></h1>
    <p class="page-hero-sub reveal reveal-delay-2">Geen losse visuals zonder vervolg. Hier zie je hoe branding, PWA's, automatisering en beheer samenkomen in trajecten die echt gebruikt worden.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="cases-main">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">Alle projecten</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1">Projecten met tractie.<br/><em>Geen showroomwerk.</em></h2>
    <div class="proof-row">
      <div class="proof-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="proof-kicker">MVP Focus</div>
        <div class="proof-value">Maatwerk trajecten</div>
        <div class="proof-copy">Voor organisaties die een serieus medewerkersportaal of maatwerk PWA nodig hebben.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="proof-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="proof-kicker">Uitrol</div>
        <div class="proof-value">White-label inzetbaar</div>
        <div class="proof-copy">Opgezet om te schalen naar meerdere teams, locaties of opdrachtgevers zonder opnieuw te beginnen.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="proof-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="proof-kicker">Volledige keten</div>
        <div class="proof-value">Design tot beheer</div>
        <div class="proof-copy">Van interface en merklaag tot hosting, onderhoud en automatisering in een doorlopend traject.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cases-full-grid">

      <a href="/case-roasted-rebels" class="case-card-full reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="case-visual"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541462608143-67571c6738dd?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Roasted Rebels" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="case-body">
          <div class="case-tag">Branding · Illustratie · Fotografie</div>
          <span class="case-status concept">Concept</span>
          <div class="case-title">Roasted Rebels</div>
          <div class="case-desc">Conceptcase die laat zien hoe branding, illustratie, fotografie en digitale presentatie als één merkervaring kunnen worden opgebouwd.</div>
          <div class="case-meta">
            <span class="case-chip">Merkidentiteit</span>
            <span class="case-chip">Illustratie</span>
            <span class="case-chip">Fotografie</span>
            <span class="case-chip">Web</span>
          </div>
          <div class="case-readmore">Bekijk volledige case →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/case-buurtapp" class="case-card-full reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="case-visual"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551650975-87deedd944c3?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="BuurtApp" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="case-body">
          <div class="case-tag">Web App · React · Firebase</div>
          <span class="case-status live">Live</span>
          <div class="case-title">BuurtApp v3.4</div>
          <div class="case-desc">Digitale buurt- en meldingsapp voor gemeentes en wijkorganisaties. Opgezet als white-label PWA met kaartmodule, dossiers, chat en statistieken.</div>
          <div class="case-meta">
            <span class="case-chip">React</span>
            <span class="case-chip">Firebase</span>
            <span class="case-chip">PWA</span>
            <span class="case-chip">Leaflet Maps</span>
          </div>
          <div class="case-readmore">Bekijk volledige case →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/case-cvw" class="case-card-full reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="case-visual"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517048676732-d65bc937f952?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Concern voor Werk" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="case-body">
          <div class="case-tag">Maatwerk MVP · Medewerkersportaal</div>
          <span class="case-status live">Live</span>
          <div class="case-title">Concern voor Werk — CVW App</div>
          <div class="case-desc">Intern portaal voor medewerkers van een sociaal werkbedrijf. Volledig maatwerk MVP met nieuws, vacatures, academie, meldpunt en admin dashboard.</div>
          <div class="case-meta">
            <span class="case-chip">React</span>
            <span class="case-chip">Firebase</span>
            <span class="case-chip">PWA</span>
            <span class="case-chip">n8n</span>
          </div>
          <div class="case-readmore">Bekijk volledige case →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/case-kluswinkel" class="case-card-full reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="case-visual"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504384308090-c894fdcc538d?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Kluswinkel App" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="case-body">
          <div class="case-tag">Planning App · Web App</div>
          <span class="case-status live">Live</span>
          <div class="case-title">Kluswinkel App v1.0</div>
          <div class="case-desc">Plannings- en werkbonnen-app die dagelijkse operatie centraliseert. Dashboard, voertuigbeheer, kijkafspraken, planning board en beheermodule in één flow.</div>
          <div class="case-meta">
            <span class="case-chip">React</span>
            <span class="case-chip">Firebase</span>
            <span class="case-chip">Planning</span>
          </div>
          <div class="case-readmore">Bekijk volledige case →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/case-webbiecorn-os" class="case-card-full reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="case-visual"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550751827-4bd374c3f58b?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Webbiecorn OS" loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="case-body">
          <div class="case-tag">AI · Automatisering · n8n</div>
          <span class="case-status lopend">Lopend</span>
          <div class="case-title">Webbiecorn OS — Intern platform</div>
          <div class="case-desc">Intern kennisplatform en automatiseringssysteem met n8n. Gericht op lead-routing, rapportages, content flows en AI-gestuurde assistentie.</div>
          <div class="case-meta">
            <span class="case-chip">n8n</span>
            <span class="case-chip">AI</span>
            <span class="case-chip">Automatisering</span>
          </div>
          <div class="case-readmore">Bekijk volledige case →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="cases-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-banner reveal">
      <h2>Ook een traject dat moet landen?</h2>
      <p>Vertel ons wat er operationeel beter moet. Dan vertalen wij dat naar een scherpe scope, passend budget en realistische eerste sprint.</p>
      <div class="btn-group">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Plan een intake</a>
        <a href="/diensten" class="btn-ghost">Bekijk budgetranges</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
